name: Sekar Bumi Tropical Farm
address: Jl. Raya Sekar Bumi No. 99 Banjar Buhu, Kerta, Kec. Payangan, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80572, Indonesia
review 1: This place really green, natural, water still fresh and the heliconia collection was really great... for me its make me refresh and get more knowledge about Heliconia... Thanks to Pak Ketut Bagia and team. Helping and explain me a lot.... weldone.
review 2: Beautiful place for outdoor activities and gathering. üëç
review 3: Beautiful place to have a fun camping time. I and three othet friends spent a night camping there and the staff were very helpful. The owner is a very polite man and cares a lot for education. A recommended place üëç
review 4:
we went to Sekar Bumi today.....the place is so natural with a lots of plants...the ivy, singgonium, phillo was so beautiful and so big healthy grew.....but one that make the day become so amazing is the monstera varigata yellow....wow......you must see it....!
but most of all the staffs are so kind and helping....they even call us when our phone and camera was left on the bike.....thank you for today..!
review 5: Very special place if you will visit it you won't waste your time. Contact them in advance please for flower workshop,  botanical excursion, dinner,  camping or collaboration
